## Citation

If you use this work in published research, please cite:

**CHAI3D:**
```bibtex
@inproceedings{conti2003chai,
  title={CHAI: An Open-Source Library for the Rapid Development of Haptic Scenes},
  author={Conti, F. and Barbagli, F. and Morris, D. and Sewell, C.},
  booktitle={IEEE World Haptics Conference},
  year={2003}
}
```

**Haply CHAI3D Integration:**
```bibtex
@inproceedings{frisson2019haply,
  title={Haply CHAI3D: Open-Source Haptic Interaction with CHAI3D},
  author={Frisson, C. and Vogel, D.},
  booktitle={Haptics: Science, Technology, and Applications (HAID)},
  year={2019}
}
```

